Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Signed-off-by: Stefan SÃ¸rensen <stefan.sorensen@spectralink.com>
Signed-off-by: Fabrice Fontaine <fontaine.fabrice@gmail.com>
